        </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Limited exceptions will ensure that complex applications can still be made using paper applications.</p>

  </div>
</div>

